        <h2 id="SpanUpHomeText" class="absolute top-[-2%]">Paket Promo</h2>
        <h1 id="HeadText" class="font-[TanGrandeur] z-10 w-full max-w-[60%] leading-[1.65] tracking-[0.04em] text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold drop-shadow-lg absolute top-[30%] transition-all duration-500">
            Celebrating Excellence, Inspiring the Future.
        </h1>
